<h3>Month 1: Foundation (Week 1 to 4)</h3>
<ul>
<li>[ ] Run a technical SEO audit and fix all issues</li>
<li>[ ] Set up Google Search Console and Google Analytics</li>
<li>[ ] Claim and optimize your Google Business Profile</li>
<li>[ ] Create email opt-in forms and a lead magnet</li>
<li>[ ] Publish 8 to 12 SEO-optimized blog posts</li>
<li>[ ] Set up 1 to 2 social media accounts</li>
<li>[ ] Submit your site to 10+ directories</li>
</ul>
<h3>Month 2: Acceleration (Week 5 to 8)</h3>
<ul>
<li>[ ] Publish 8 to 12 more blog posts (target 20+ total)</li>
<li>[ ] Send weekly emails to your growing list</li>
<li>[ ] Share every blog post on social media</li>
<li>[ ] Write 2 to 3 guest posts with backlinks</li>
<li>[ ] Start participating in 2 online communities</li>
